  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Build panels for nightstand frame",
      "body": "Build 4 panels for the nightstand frame by joining three 1x5 boards each using 1-1/4\"pocket hole screws and wood glue. You will have two panels that are 16\" tall and two panels that are 14 7/8\" tall.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/c221422bbb90e47c.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Build the frame",
      "body": "Build the box for the nightstand frame by joining the four panels using 1-1/4\"pocket hole screws and wood glue. The pocket holes are on both ends of the 14 7/8\" panels. Using corner clamps makes it easy to ensure that the box is square.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/fc5b456f81b5ffb8.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Build front/back legs",
      "body": "Attach the angled apron between two legs using 2-1/2\" pocket holes screws and wood glue. Build two of these.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/77eff02ea5aa41a4.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Attach straight aprons",
      "body": "Attach both the straight aprons to one of the leg frames built in the above step using 2-1/2\" pocket hole screws and wood glue.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/131b1956cce7a45f.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Build final leg frame",
      "body": "Attach the second leg frame using 2-1/2\" pocket hole screws and wood glue to get get the final leg frame for the nightstand.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/21b7b1e19a82b93b.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Attach legs to the nightstand frame",
      "body": "Align the nightstand box on the frame. The front legs are aligned with the front of the box. There is 1\" spacing from each side. Attach using 1-1/4\" wood screws all around from the inside of the nightstand frame.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/75796664d5e6cde2.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Build Drawers",
      "body": "Build two drawers using the 1x6 boards and install drawer slides inside the nightstand frame. Attach the 1x8 drawer frames and your choice of hardware.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/607bc0036643eca3.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "See more information",
      "body": "For more details on this project, please see - https://www.anikasdiylife.com/diy-nightstand-with-drawers/\nFor a full video of the build - https://youtu.be/LO3aQBazBiU"
    }
  ],
